import React from 'react'; const Welcome = ({ onD3React, onQGIS, onFinish }) => { return (

HI!

The data visualization is about travel experience with different transportation modes.

The static map and interactive map data visualization were created and developed by Quantum Geographic Information System (QGIS) software and D3.js with React respectively.



In this visualization, you can find the data regarding HRV, HR_mad, stress level, and journey satisfaction score during the travel.

You need to explore BOTH of THE MAPS by yourself to gain the information as much as you can. There is no limited time in this experiment, and you can make your own notes.

You can choose the button which map you want to dive first, and you can click the "back button" to change your next map.



If you think you are done, you can click the "Finish" button below to answer the questionnaire.



Once you click finish, you cannot go back again.





); }; export default Welcome;
